import React from 'react'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Header from './components/Header'
import HeaderCarousel from './components/HeaderCarousel'
import HomeScreenCard from './components/HomeScreenCard'
import HomeScreenCardItem from './components/HomeScreenCardItem'
import './App.css'
import HomeScreenMap from './components/HomeScreenMap'
import HomeScreenNav from './components/HomeScreenNav'
import HomeScreenCountryName from './components/HomeScreenCountryName'
import Footer from './components/Footer'
import HomeScreenCapitalDetail from './components/HomeScreenCapitalDetail'
import SecondScreenCard from './secondscreen/SecondScreenCard'
import SecondScreenHeader from './secondscreen/SecondScreenHeader'
import ThirdScreen from './thirdscreen/ThirdScreen'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
const App = () => {
    return (
        <Router>
            <Header/>
            <Route path={['/','/:name']} component={HeaderCarousel} exact/>
            <Route path={['/','/:name']} component={HomeScreenNav} exact/>
            <Route path="/" component={HomeScreenCountryName} exact/>
            <Route path="/" component={HomeScreenCapitalDetail} exact/>
            <Route path="/" component={HomeScreenCardItem} exact/>
            <Route path="/" component={HomeScreenCardItem} exact/>
            <Route path="/" component={HomeScreenMap} exact/>
            <Route />

            <Route path={['/','/:name']} component={Footer} exact/>  

          
        </Router>
    )
}

export default App
